{"tid":1832161,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"幾時先搞班死人支那代購撚呀？","createTime":"2020-01-21T03:32:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T05:46:17.000Z","uid":107157,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"852917d6a7816cb0ee52877e486f42fd3863843b","tid":1832161,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:32:23.000Z","msg":"支那代購撚: 香港是中国的<br />\n之後就消費一國兩制去搵錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個個月出4次海關就賺幾皮野<br />\n你同我日日捱ot就得果皮幾野<br />\n<br />\n根據我觀察，啲代購撚主要以下既要點:<br />\n<br />\n1。一星期通常星期六，日先過海關，因為大部分支那蟲都有正職。<br />\n<br />\n2。必經黨鐵站: 九龍塘，羅湖/落馬洲<br />\n<br />\n3。朝早出，夜晚返<br />\n<br />\n整合以上重點，最合適既策略就係星期六，日封殺東鐵線既轉乘站! <br />\n<br />\n和理遊車河: 全世界坐黨鐵東鐵線不斷循環坐唔落車，但班人上唔到車。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家有冇咩高見?"},{"pid":"598369c7aa3dbe92f22420e96c4585f703607a2c","tid":1832161,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:34:48.000Z","msg":"好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又比班代購狗串"},{"pid":"4070ac4ae9fca8f475e993817073239a1647100c","tid":1832161,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:35:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4c73cf620da0770896dae185c768efc75890c5fd","tid":1832161,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4070ac4ae9fca8f475e993817073239a1647100c","tid":1832161,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:35:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:37:04.000Z","msg":"幾時100% 破埋代購撚呀"},{"pid":"a144332e30de59065070123a7549beade3e1b342","tid":1832161,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:38:07.000Z","msg":"定係連登仔本身就係代購撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hk